OL,3,CTeachers' unions asked to suspend
OL,4,Cindustrial action
OL,6,FThe teachers' unions have been asked
OL,7,Fby Stormont Education Minister Paul
OL,8,FGivan to suspend industrial action.
OL,10,FTeachers have taken part in strikes
OL,11,Fover an outstanding pay award, as well
OL,12,Fas long-running action short of strike
OL,13,Fover conditions.
OL,15,FMr Givan met with representatives of
OL,16,Fthe Northern Ireland Teachers'
OL,17,FCouncil, including NASUWT, INTO, UTU,
OL,18,FNEU and NAHT(NI), on Tuesday.
