OL,6,FHe described a "positive engagement",
OL,7,Fand said they discussed their "shared
OL,8,Fobjective of a quick resolution to the
OL,9,Fongoing pay dispute".
OL,11,FMr Givan also spoke of his concern at
OL,12,Fthe impact of industrial action on
OL,13,Fpupils, and said he asked the unions
OL,14,Fto suspend it.
OL,16,F"Teachers fully deserve a fair and
OL,17,Fappropriate pay settlement, and I will
OL,18,Fwork to deliver that.
OL,20,F"It is rightly of the highest
OL,21,Fpriority," he said.
