OL,6,F"I am greatly concerned about the
OL,7,Fdetrimental impact continued action is
OL,8,Fhaving on the education of pupils,
OL,9,Fincluding our most vulnerable children
OL,10,Fand young people.
OL,12,F"In view of this, and in the context
OL,13,Fof the opportunity before us to
OL,14,Fresolve outstanding issues, I asked
OL,15,Fthe unions to suspend industrial
OL,16,Faction, including action short of
OL,17,Fstrike, to allow negotiations to take
OL,18,Fplace in a more positive atmosphere."
