OL,6,FMr Givan said he is committed to
OL,7,Fworking with Executive colleagues to
OL,8,Faddress public sector pay issues.
OL,10,F"I want to create the environment
OL,11,Fwhereby meaningful pay negotiations
OL,12,Fthrough the Teachers' Negotiating
OL,13,FCommittee (TNC) can commence," he
OL,14,Fadded.
